{"tid":2294243,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"向美展實力 警告拜登勿反華","createTime":"2020-11-21T01:11:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T01:54:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5d1c673af0bf71ef57164c9ac7095ed0868f7e98","tid":2294243,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T01:11:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201121/HP3JLKJYV5CNZA7A55HVGW5RII/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201121%2FHP3JLKJYV5CNZA7A55HVGW5RII%2F&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM3y1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=4e76475e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201121%2FHP3JLKJYV5CNZA7A55HVGW5RII%2F&h=7ef30c83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201121/HP3JLKJYV5CNZA7A55HVGW5RII/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n向美展實力 警告拜登勿反華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hiJQMJ8F7HqHKpeVxYPt5eDbsag=/1770x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SZVWEAPYBVCZFLYYN3N35RJUVA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhiJQMJ8F7HqHKpeVxYPt5eDbsag%3D%2F1770x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSZVWEAPYBVCZFLYYN3N35RJUVA.jpg&h=111a2edf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■大馬官員聚首吉隆坡觀看亞太經合組織網上峯會直播。<br />\n<br />\n【拆 局】【本報訊】中國問題專家林和立指出，習近平在中國和日韓澳紐及東盟十國簽定ＲＣＥＰ後，首度表明有意加入TPP 2.0，是在美國政權交接之際向美國展示實力，警告拜登若繼續特朗普的反華政策，中國有實力將美國排除於亞太經貿之外。不過，有學者指出，亞太經貿未來數年的發展「不是中國，也不是美國」領軍，日本與南韓反成為主力軍。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：趁拜登亞太貿易政策未明朗出招  習謀加入CPTPP做一哥<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n顧忌拜登多邊主義<br />\n<br />\n林和立指出，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n所以，習近平昨強調，中國簽定RCEP後，考慮加入TPP 2.0，向美國展示實力。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n華盛頓智庫傳統基金會亞洲研究中心專研亞洲經濟的學者沃爾特斯（Riley Walters）則估計日韓未來亞太經貿走向。他表示，對東盟來說，中國是第一大貿易夥伴，但這些國家對中國從來就有各自不同的忌憚；RCEP是涵蓋範圍大的貿易協定，但標準不高。他認為，未來幾年亞太將是日本與韓國閃耀的時代。"},{"pid":"6c7ad0b9a0cf432c6e8e4417bc12e218c31c21a4","tid":2294243,"uid":183758,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T01:32:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g63UYky.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg63UYky.gif&h=30968f59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5tyqkyU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5tyqkyU.jpg&h=ee08c9ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9666ada41c29bb0e9dcc12c6c0d7489db17d2d2e","tid":2294243,"uid":290393,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6c7ad0b9a0cf432c6e8e4417bc12e218c31c21a4","tid":2294243,"uid":183758,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T01:32:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g63UYky.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg63UYky.gif&h=30968f59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5tyqkyU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5tyqkyU.jpg&h=ee08c9ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T01:49:03.000Z","msg":"中國個做法係強硬野蠻，因為呢個係打死多邊主義最好方法，如果美國仲要尋求盟友先敢講野，其他盟友更唔會出頭<br />\n<br />\n美國果班死白痴左膠到時就會唔出聲，拉去講地球環保同南極冰山之類野<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f69a2f15dbd1dcf8c218dba6f9f9c52ce7ead8","tid":2294243,"uid":183758,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9666ada41c29bb0e9dcc12c6c0d7489db17d2d2e","tid":2294243,"uid":290393,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6c7ad0b9a0cf432c6e8e4417bc12e218c31c21a4","tid":2294243,"uid":183758,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T01:32:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g63UYky.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg63UYky.gif&h=30968f59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5tyqkyU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5tyqkyU.jpg&h=ee08c9ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},"